::Hot Rod::

He kept his eyes on Unicron. Unicron hadn't done anything even now that
he was facing Hot Rod and Ultra Magnus.

::Epyon::

He searched the battle field. Things were settaling down. They would
have to start construction of the city soon.

::DrillBit::

He pulled back. Looking at the bots still at the battle.
He found Killfest.
"Well, think we proved our intentions to the Alliance and all?"

::Dollon::

He just stayed at DrillBit's side, not opening his mouth as usual.

::Demolition::

He smiled as he saw FZ return. Now Zardus would deal with this Wolfgang.

::KitKat2::

She woundered around the base some more. She came apon Zardus. She
stayed quiet observing what was happaning.
